.ident	"@(#)niccfg:help/slot_number	1.1"
.related /dev/null
.title Slot Number Help Screen 
 You must now select the slot number in which your Network 
 Card is configured.  To display the list of choices, press <F2>. 

 If you are unsure of this value, you should shut down 
 your system now and follow the manufacturer's instructions 
 on how to find the SLOT number for your network card. 

 EXITING HELP 
 Press <Esc> to return to the Network Interface 
 Card Configuration Screen. 
